FT  13 JUN 92 / Finance and the Family (Briefcase): Interesting request
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
ON LEAVING, one of my furnished tenants is not only claiming the return of
the deposit but also interest thereon. There is no mention of interest being
paid in the agreement. Can he claim it?
The claim for interest is not justified by law.
